---
title: Mushroom & Zucchini Tempura Bowls with Sesame Scallion Rice, Quick-Pickled Cucumber & Sweet Heat Sauce
description: One of our favorite ways to eat our veggies? Giving them the tempura treatment! Coating them in the light, airy batter before frying yields addictively crispy, golden results you just can’t get any other way. Here, you’ll whip up tempura mushrooms and zucchini, then pile into rice bowls with tangy pickled cucumber, sesame seeds, and chili flakes. It’s all drizzled with chili mayo for creamy, spicy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-zucchini-tempura-bowls-e73a42e2.jpg
